Akropolis 275: Modern Luxury Residences in Geroskipou, Paphos

Akropolis 275 is a sophisticated residential development nestled on the serene outskirts of Paphos, in the lively town of Geroskipou. This exclusive project showcases beautifully designed apartments that combine spacious interiors with expansive balconies and sun-drenched terraces, all complemented by secure covered parking.

Positioned in a peaceful yet highly accessible area, these homes are just a short drive from the bustling Paphos city center, where residents can enjoy a wide variety of shops, cafes, and essential services. Nearby landmarks include Iasis Hospital and the prestigious Neapolis University, ensuring everyday conveniences are within easy reach. Additionally, Paphos International Airport is conveniently located just ten minutes away, making travel simple and efficient.

Akropolis 275 offers a premium selection of luxurious two- and three-bedroom apartments, making it an ideal choice for permanent living. Each residence is designed with thoughtful features, including private landscaped gardens, communal green spaces, covered parking areas, and a modern lift system for effortless accessibility. This development perfectly blends contemporary style with practical living, providing an exceptional opportunity for those seeking upscale real estate in Paphos.

Description EN:
Armonia Beach Villas: Contemporary Coastal Homes in Kissonerga, Paphos

Discover Armonia Beach Villas, a refined residential enclave tucked away in the tranquil seaside area of Kissonerga. Located just a few kilometers north of Paphos, beyond the quaint charm of Kissonerga Village, this exclusive development offers a stunning setting overlooking a peaceful coastal bay.

Ideally situated between the lively Paphos Harbour and the iconic Coral Bay Beach, Armonia Beach Villas delivers an exceptional lifestyle defined by comfort, elegance, and natural beauty. Crafted with precision and attention to detail, each villa blends luxury with functionality, featuring private swimming pools surrounded by beautifully landscaped gardens. Generous verandas, BBQ areas, and open-air living spaces provide the perfect environment for entertaining and relaxation alike.

With a focus on modern design, each villa incorporates cutting-edge technologies and premium finishes that reflect a timeless sense of style. The architecture is sleek yet welcoming, designed to enhance both aesthetics and practicality. Spacious driveways and ample parking ensure added convenience for homeowners and their guests. Armonia Beach Villas is more than a home—it’s a coastal retreat where sophisticated living meets the serenity of the Mediterranean.

Wyróżniające się nowoczesnymi projektami architektonicznymi, nasyconymi najnowszymi technologiami i wykończeniami premium, Armonia Beach Villas emanują ponadczasową elegancją. Description RU:

Идеально расположенные между оживленным портом Пафоса и завораживающим пляжем Корал-Бэй, Armonia Beach Villas представляют собой поистине исключительный опыт проживания. Наличие зон для барбекю и просторных веранд с жилыми зонами на открытом воздухе еще больше усиливает привлекательность этих домов.

Отличающиеся современным архитектурным дизайном, оснащенным новейшими технологиями и премиальной отделкой, Armonia Beach Villas излучают вечную элегантность.
